schools.name: David C Hinson Sr Middle School

data.description: Come see this Charming concrete block home with 3 bedroom 2 bathroom house with fully fenced yard and a He/She shed or work shop. House was updated about 3 years ago. Kitchen, Bath, AC, Windows, Storm shutters and more. Livingroom has a wood burning fireplace and the kitchen has a nice island with SS Appliances. Washer and Dryer are also included. There's a new roof installed November 2023. Also this house has a Water softener and Solar Panels for a low electric bill. Close to major highways, Fine Dining, Hospitals, Shopping and don't forget the Beach. "And $5,000 sellers concession for closing costs."
